free: #e A child had a pet frog.
#c 一個小孩養了一隻青蛙。
#e He put the frog in the container.
#e The boy and the dog went to sleep.
#e The frog (jumped) out (of the container) and went away.
#c 那青蛙(從瓶子裡)出來四處遊蕩。
#e The boy and the dog got up.
#e (The boy) has looked for the frog everywhere.
#e (He) went by the window and called at the frog.
#e They continuously looked for the frog. The dog fell (from the window).
#c 他們一直找青蛙。狗（從窗戶）掉下去。
#e (The container) where the frog had been kept broke.
#e They proceeded again to look for the frog.
#c 他們又繼續去遠一點找青蛙。
#e The boy called toward the ground.
#e He called the frog through the hole in the ground. And the dog
#c 他對著地上的洞叫青蛙。而那隻狗..
#e The child moved toward the hole in the ground, and it was a house of mouse.
#c 小孩去那個地上的洞，原來那是老鼠的家。
#e What the dog look up toward was a beehive. The dog shook the tree (with the beehive.
#c 小狗往上看的那個目標是蜂窩。小狗搖那樹。
#e The beehive partly separated (from the tree). (The bees) scattered.
#c 蜂窩部分脫離了(樹)。(蜂)四散開來。
#e (The child) looked toward the hole in the tree.
#e (He) got frightened, and called the frog. (The owl) came out. The boy got frightened.
#c (他)嚇到，叫青蛙。(貓頭鷹)出來，小孩子嚇一跳。
#e  (The beehive) shaken and falling down the ground chased the dog.
#c 被搖下來的蜂還是一直追狗。
#e He wanted to hide from the owl which had kept chasing him.
#c 他想要躲開那一直追他的貓頭鷹
#e The boy climbed on something bulging.
#e (He) kept on calling for the frog.
#e The deer got frightened and carried him and ran toward the cliff.
#c 那隻鹿嚇到了，就帶著他跑向懸崖。
#n 助動詞 mi-si 應是講錯，應為i-si。Aux mi-si should be corrected as i-si.

#e The deer shook down the child.
#e The boy and the dog fell, and happen to fell into the water.
#c 小孩和狗掉下來，剛好掉到有水的地方。
#e They fell into the water and they heard like the sound of a frog.
#c 他們掉到水裡聽到像青蛙的（聲音）。
#e  The boy told the dog not to be noisy. (The boy said): 'I seem to hear a frog (croaking).'
#c 小孩不准小狗吵，(小孩說)：我好像聽到青蛙（叫）。
#e A tree happened to be there.
#e They looked for the frog around the tree.
#c 他們在樹的周圍找青蛙。
#e (The boy suddenly realized that）it was together with (another frogs).
#c 原來有其他青蛙在一起。
#e (The frog) was together (with the other frogs).
#c 那隻青蛙和其他青蛙在一起。
